第六代野马于2013年12月5日分别在[[迪尔伯恩|迪尔伯恩]]、[[纽约|纽约]]、[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]、[[巴塞罗那|巴塞罗那]]、[[上海|上海]]，以及[[悉尼|悉尼]]亮相。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.autoblog.com/2013/11/19/2015-ford-mustang-world-debut-december-5-video/ |title=2015 Ford Mustang to make world debut on Dec. 5 |first=Seyth |last=Miersma |date=November 19, 2013 |website=autoblog.com |accessdate=February 26, 2014 |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806101517/https://www.autoblog.com/2013/11/19/2015-ford-mustang-world-debut-december-5-video/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>该内部项目代号为S-550。

这代野马的改变包括了1.5英寸加宽车身和1.4英寸下车身、梯形水箱罩、2.75英寸的低行李箱盖，以及新颜色选项。乘客量提升至了84.5平方英尺，并有三种引擎选项：314匹马力的2.3升 Ecoboost [[直列四缸引擎|四缸]]、300匹马力的3.7升 [[V6发动机|V6]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.autoblog.com/2014/07/17/2015-ford-mustang-specs-435-hp/ |title=2015 Ford Mustang specs revealed, GT to pack 435 HP |first=Greg |last=Migliore |work=Auto blog |date=July 17, 2014 |accessdate=July 18, 2014 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112020754/https://www.autoblog.com/2014/07/17/2015-ford-mustang-specs-435-hp/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，或435匹马力的5.0升 郊狼[[V8发动机|V8]]，变速箱方面配置了[[格特拉克传动系统有限公司|格特拉克]]6前速[[手动变速箱|手排]]或配有换挡拨片的6前速[[自动变速箱|自排]]。<ref>{{cite journal|title=The World's 'Stang |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_autoweek_2013-12-09_63_25/page/24 |last=Vettraino |first=J.P.|journal=Autoweek |date=December 9, 2013|pages=24–29}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.autoblog.com/2013/12/05/2015-ford-mustang-official-photos-reveal-info/ |title=2015 Ford Mustang GT |first=Brandon |last=Turkus |date=December 5, 2013 |website=autoblog.com |accessdate=December 14, 2013 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124072725/https://www.autoblog.com/2013/12/05/2015-ford-mustang-official-photos-reveal-info/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |url=https://media.ford.com/content/fordmedia/fna/us/en/asset.download.document.pdf.html/content/dam/fordmedia/North%20America/US/2015_Specs/Mustang_Specs_USA.pdf |title=2015 Ford Mustang USA Specifications |website=media.ford |format=PDF |date= |accessdate=February 26, 2014 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304000456/https://media.ford.com/content/fordmedia/fna/us/en/asset.download.document.pdf.html/content/dam/fordmedia/North%20America/US/2015_Specs/Mustang_Specs_USA.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>新介绍的Ecoboost 四缸引擎开发出了能实现高关税的全球市场，如中国。 <ref>{{cite news |title=Ford Mustang in China Has Smaller Engine, Bigger Price |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/09/business/international/japan-seeks-to-squelch-its-tiny-cars.html?_r=0 |newspaper=The New York Times |date=June 9, 2014 |accessdate=February 17, 2015 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111203008/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/09/business/international/japan-seeks-to-squelch-its-tiny-cars.html?_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年野马采用了专为新车型开发的新[[独立悬吊系统|独立后悬吊系统]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.goauto.com.au/mellor/mellor.nsf/story2/4F1A71B114AEAC87CA257C38007D744B |title=Ford Mustang remains All-American |publisher=GoAuto |date=December 6, 2013 |accessdate=January 8, 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107151531/http://www.goauto.com.au/mellor/mellor.nsf/story2/4F1A71B114AEAC87CA257C38007D744B |dead-url=no }}</ref>

本代野马因海外左侧行驶汽车市场需求成为原厂设计的第一版左侧行驶版野马。在该款式年份，左侧行驶版野马扩展到了新的出口市场。

本代野马因为在正面，侧面和翻转碰撞保护方面，于2015年2月被美国国家公路交通安全管理局评为5星。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.safercar.gov/Vehicle+Shoppers/5-Star+Safety+Ratings/2011-Newer+Vehicles/Vehicle-Detail?vehicleId=9555 |title=2015 Ford Mustang 2 DR RWD |publisher=National Highway Traffic Safety Administration (NHTSA) |accessdate=January 2, 2016 |archive-date=2020-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731180214/https://www.safercar.gov/Vehicle+Shoppers/5-Star+Safety+Ratings/2011-Newer+Vehicles/Vehicle-Detail?vehicleId=9555 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

福特于2015年2月发布召回2014年2月14日至2015年2月10日间在弗拉特洛克装配厂生产的2.3升 涡轮增压四缸引擎版野马。而截止2015年6月，有100万台野马因高田株式会社的气囊影响而被召回。这次召回发生在高田因气囊可能爆炸或爆出金属碎片而召回338万美国野马后。<ref>Ford includes 1 million Mustangs and GTs in Takata airbag recall[http://www.mlive.com/auto/index.ssf/2015/06/ford_adds_1_million_mustangs_a.html] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mlive.com/auto/index.ssf/2015/06/ford_adds_1_million_mustangs_a.html |date=20180912043152 }}</ref>

==謝爾比野馬==

{{main|謝爾比野馬}}

由福特的有聯繫的改裝車廠的高性能亞品牌，屬於[[超級跑車|超級跑車]]而非[[肌肉車|肌肉車]]或[[小馬車|小馬車]]等級的性能。

==歐洲生產版==

{{main|{{tsl|en|Ford Capri|福特Capri}}}}

稱為Capri的野馬歐洲子車系，是在1969-1985年間生產，車身大小和原始的野馬一樣屬於[[中型車|中型車]]，比同期美國的野馬小，而發動機的排氣量降至1.3-3公升間，僅有[[小型車|小型車]]至中型車的級數。因為後來美國的野馬都降到中型車級數，而小於兩公升的[[自然進氣發動機|自然進氣發動機]]又無法為本車提供跑車所標榜的性能，而在八十年代中停產了。

